The game was met with positive to average reception. [[GameRankings]] and [[Metacritic]] gave it a score of 73% and 74 out of 100 for the [[PlayStation (console)|PlayStation]] version,<ref name=GRPS/><ref name=MCPS/> and 68% and 75 out of 100 for the [[PlayStation 2]] version.<ref name=GRPS2/><ref name=MCPS2/>
